trans-unit.source: Defines the friendly name for a property of a Web Parts control.
trans-unit.target: 웹 파트 컨트롤의 속성에 대 한 알기 쉬운 이름을 정의합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart> control provides a generic user interface (UI) that enables users to edit custom properties on <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> and server controls placed in <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> zones.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart>컨트롤은 사용자가을 사용자 지정 속성을 편집할 수 있도록 하는 일반 사용자 인터페이스 (UI) <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>서버 컨트롤에 배치 하 고 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>영역.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The editing UI is provided for properties that are marked in the source code with the `WebBrowsable` attribute (from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebBrowsableAttribute> class).
trans-unit.target: 편집 UI로 소스 코드에 표시 된 속성을 위해 제공 됩니다는 `WebBrowsable` 특성 (에서 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebBrowsableAttribute>클래스).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebBrowsableAttribute>

trans-unit.source: When a property is marked with this attribute, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart> control creates the editing UI based on the type of the property, and uses a <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> object if needed to convert the value in each editing control to the type of the property.
trans-unit.target: 속성은이 특성으로 표시 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart>컨트롤 속성의 형식에 따라 편집 UI에서 만들고 사용 하는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>개체 각 편집 컨트롤의 값 속성의 형식으로 변환 하는 데 필요한 경우.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The `WebDisplayName` attribute (from the WebDisplayNameAttribute class) allows you to specify the text for the label that appears with each control in the editing UI.
trans-unit.target: `WebDisplayName` (WebDisplayNameAttribute 클래스)에서 특성을 사용 하면 편집 UI의 각 컨트롤과 함께 표시 되는 레이블에 대 한 텍스트를 지정할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute"></xref> class without a specified name.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute"> </xref> 지정 된 이름이 없는 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The WebDisplayNameAttribute constructor sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A> property to an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: WebDisplayNameAttribute 생성자 집합은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A>속성을 빈 문자열 ("").</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute"></xref> class with a specified display name.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute"> </xref> 지정 된 표시 이름 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The WebDisplayNameAttribute constructor sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A> property to `displayName`.
trans-unit.target: WebDisplayNameAttribute 생성자 집합은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A>속성을 `displayName`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The `displayName` parameter is the value that will appear in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart> control.
trans-unit.target: `displayName` 매개 변수는 값에 표시 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart>컨트롤.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart>

trans-unit.source: The friendly name to use in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 이름에서 사용 하는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Represents an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute"></xref> class with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName*> property set to an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: 인스턴스를 나타내며는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute"> </xref> 클래스와 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName*>속성이 빈 문자열로 설정 ("").</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName*>

trans-unit.source: The Default field returns the same result as calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: 호출할 때와 동일한 결과 반환 하는 기본 필드는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.%23ctor%2A>생성자.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: 추가할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of a property to display in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 에 표시할 속성의 이름을 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"> </xref> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>에 표시할 값을 포함 하는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"> </xref>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name to display in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: 에 표시할 이름을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"> </xref> 제어 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The DisplayNameValue property gets or sets the same value that is accessed through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: DisplayNameValue 속성 통해 액세스 하는 것과 동일한 값을 가져오거나는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A>속성.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebDisplayNameAttribute.DisplayName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The DisplayNameValue property is protected and therefore only accessible either within the class or through a derived class.
trans-unit.target: DisplayNameValue 속성이 보호 되 고 따라서 클래스 또는 파생된 클래스를 통해 액세스할 수 없기 때문입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the value to display in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.String>에 표시할 값을 포함 하는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PropertyGridEditorPart"> </xref>.</xref:System.String>
